  "description": "Howdy folks! I have an important update to start with:\nThe \u0026ldquo;emspeculation\u0026rdquo; newsletter, which I started earlier in the month, is ending, really before it got off the ground. Stripe won\u0026rsquo;t verify my account, so there\u0026rsquo;s no way for me to do a paid and private newsletter. Luckily, it\u0026rsquo;s only the accounts associated with that newsletter that seem to have been affected - my primary Stripe account is still active!\n",
